'''Mutiganda Janvier''' (wavutse ku ya 18 Ukwakira 1989), ni umukinnyi wa filime mu [[Rwanda]] wagize uruhare runini nk'umwanditsi wa sinema ndetse na producer muri filime nyinshi zica kuri televiziyo.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/193156</ref> 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 18 Ukwakira 1989 i [[Kigali]], mu Rwanda<ref>https://rwandamagazine.com/inkuru-zamamaza/article/ingingo-z-ingenzi-z-urwandiko-rwa-mutiganda-janvier-rusaba-guhindura-izina</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2013, yarangije icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza mu buhinzi. Icyakora yaje kwimukira mubakinnyi ba firime no gukora film kubera ishyaka rye rya sinema<ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.person.mutiganda-wa-nkunda.49886.html</ref>. Nyuma muri uwo mwaka, amashusho ye 4 yambere yerekana ibihimbano yashyizwe ku rutonde mu marushanwa ya Global Dialogues Amateka magufi yo gukora amarushanwa<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/111022/ihuriro-ryabanditsi-ba-filime-ryashimye-mutiganda-wa-nkunda-wahesheje-ishema-u-rwanda-muri-111022.html</ref> .  Muri 2014, yanditse, atunganya kandi ayobora filime ye ya mbere ya ''Rayila'' , Ninkuru yumubyeyi wataye umwana we akiyahura. Iyi filime yamamaye cyane kandi yegukana ibihembo mu birori byinshi bya firime ndetse no mu mamahanga<ref>http://africultures.com/evenements/?no=39350</ref>. 

Muri 2014 kandi, yanditse sitcom izwi cyane ''Inshuti yanyuze'' kuri TV 10 mu [[Rwanda]] hagati ya 2014 na 2015. Ifatwa nkurukurikirane rwa mbere rwa TV rwakozwe mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://eastafricamonitor.com/rwanda-shrugs-off-us-trade-war-blow-turns-to-europe/</ref>. Yasohotse kandi kuri YouTube kandi yakira abafana benshi.  Muri 2015, Janvier yakoze nka producer kuri firime ngufi ''Ishaba'' yakozwe mu mahugurwa yo gukina amafilime yakozwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema nyafurika rya Mashariki (MAAFF)<ref>https://agakiza.org/Menya-byinshi-kuri-filime-yakinwe-ku-buzima-bwa-Yesu.html</ref>. Amashusho yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime kandi asohoka kuri DVD na Africalia mu rwego rwo gukusanya filime ngufi za Afurika nziza<ref>https://beautifulrwanda.org/2021/08/01/rwanda-shrugs-its-shoulders-and-turns-to-europe/</ref>. Nyuma y'umwaka, yagiye mu mahugurwa yo kwandika filimi ya Maisha Film Lab i [[Kigali]], aho yakoraga nk'umwanditsi kuri series zizwi cyane zisetsa ''Seburikoko zanyuze'' kuri televiziyo y'u [[Rwanda]] muri Werurwe 2015<ref>https://gazettes.africa/archive/rw/2017/rw-government-gazette-dated-2017-07-24-no-30.pdf</ref>. Hagati aho, yakoraga akazi ko gutunganya filime n’umunyamakuru kuva mu 2013 mu bitangazamakuru byinshi byaho.  Nyuma yaje gukora firime ngufi, ''La Femme Nue'' yatoranijwe kunshuro ya 3 muri MAAFF<ref>https://rwanda.shafaqna.com/FR/AL/242055</ref>. 

Nyuma yo kuva mu mwuga w’abanyamakuru mu 2016, yibanze cyane ku gukina amafilime aho yayoboye ibiganiro bya TV ''City Maid'' kuri ubu bica kuri Televiziyo y’u [[Rwanda]]. Muri icyo gihe, yakoze serial ya ''Virunga School'' yerekana kuri TV<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/208565</ref>.  Hanyuma yanditse, akora kandi ayobora film ye ya kabiri ngufi ''Ibanga ry'umunezero'' muri 2017. Hagati aho, yashinze isosiyete yigenga itunganya firime yitwa 'IZACU'<ref>https://www.archyde.com/this-film-is-my-story-and-that-of-other-young-people-who-are-fighting-to-survive-in-kigali/</ref>. Muri iyi sosiyete, yakoze filime ye ya mbere yise Nameless nyuma ayishyira mu mahugurwa ya Takmil ya Carthage Film Festival 2018<ref>https://maishafilmlab.org/maisha-alumni/mutiganda-wa-nkunda/</ref>. Muri aya mahugurwa, iyi filime yaguzwe n’igihangange cya Orange Studio y’Abafaransa kandi iyi filime ikaba yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Friborg mu [[Ubusuwisi|Busuwisi]]<ref>https://cinidb.africa/Professionals/Details/53</ref>. Nk'umuproducer, yakoze  A Taste of our Land yatsindiye ibihembo byambere bya firime nziza muri PanAfrican Film Festival 2020 na AMAAs 2021<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/author/16</ref>. 

